            "detailed_description": "Play as the mysterious new character TSYGAN, a rogue insurgent that joins the Core Guardians in defending the only enclave of humanity left on the planet LOEK III. Road to Elysion features a new area to explore with four new maps, new unlockable towers, weapons and perks! This DLC is the first out of four contained in the Sanctum 2 Season Pass.<br><br><strong>Note:</strong> Road to Elysion is included in the Sanctum 2 <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/237190/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Season Pass</a> and is part 1/4 in a series of DLC for Sanctum 2<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Playable Character - TSYGAN, the “Rogue Insurgent”<br></li><li>4 New Unique Maps – adding refreshing new tactics and replayability.<br></li><li>2 Weapons - Rapid-firing Gatling Laser &amp; TSYGANs own handheld Ballista!<br></li><li>2 Towers - Range Spire that dramatically increases the range of nearby offensive towers and the Slow Field Dispenser letting you strengthen your choke points further!<br></li><li>Enhanced Enemies - From new support monsters that heal and mutate the attacking horde to a brand new aerial enemy boss, players should be prepared for this heightened challenge.<br></li><li>Additional Perks – Customize your character even more with six new perks, including a perk that gives you an in-game pet robot that will fight for you!</li></ul>",
